#### Git Ignore File for ESATAN TMS Materials Database ####

# INITIAL POLICY - Ignore All Files in Orbiter 2016 Directory
*

# Track LICENSE and this Git Ignore
!LICENSE
!.gitignore

# Track Orbiter Core & Addon Configurations
## Orbiter 2016 Core
!Orbiter_NG.cfg
## D3D9 Graphics Client
!D3D9Client.cfg
## XRSound Module
!XRSound/
!XRSound/XRSound.cfg
## XR1 DeltaGlider Module
!Config/
!Config/DeltaGliderXR1Prefs.cfg

# Track GMAT Mission Scripts and Documentation
## Top Level Subfolders and Mission Index
!GMAT/
!GMAT/**
## Exclude GMAT Script Backups in Subfolders
GMAT/*/*.bak
